AI AGENT DISCLAIMER

This software is designed to provide domain expertise to AI agents, including
but not limited to Claude Code, GitHub Copilot, OpenAI Codex, and Gemini CLI.
The creators and contributors of this plugin are not responsible for any
actions taken by AI agents that consume this plugin's skills, agents, or
knowledge content. Users are solely responsible for reviewing, validating, and
approving any output, recommendations, code, configurations, or actions
produced or taken by AI agents using this plugin.

This plugin is currently in beta experimentation mode and should not be used
in production environments without proper testing, validation, and human
oversight. The knowledge and recommendations provided by this plugin are
informational only and do not constitute professional advice. Always verify
AI-generated output against official documentation and apply changes through
proper change management processes.
